Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:34.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:37.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.99,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
