Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到黑龙竟然和「Fang」勾结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追击队还没准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编队得花些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  我们去救萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  对方可是黑龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们能对抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来你还动不了才对  真是够顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气的表情也很美啊  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是药  喝下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让人绑架我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  毫无戒备地跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一被人类抓到你该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你监视着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为红龙的结界太坚固  我进不去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你做我的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是黑龙一族代代相传的婚约之证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西有着契约之力  只有我能拆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的所在地也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲斐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发信器  做好迎击准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尼基斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要我做新娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想和你订下契约
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让龙之力真正觉醒的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有与真心信任的人才能进行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  可以得到压倒一切的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已经很强了吗  为什么还想要力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到所有遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是龙的追求  你不能理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的东西只有一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟你订契约  放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会成为一个好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我城里来吧  碍事的人是进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那慢慢培养感情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是打算就这样不了了之？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着萝丝不管？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐还不是要把萝丝交给「Society」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不一样  我们被萝丝救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是不明白那孩子自愿跟奥尼基斯走的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保护我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是为了保护你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心很痛吧  那是因为萝丝不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再好好考虑一下吧  萝丝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被萝丝救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把萝丝救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那就说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说龙司不帮忙的话  我也想不出救萝丝的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想到什么办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪来的密码？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的是S级的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我完全用不上的特级道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面也有着被诅咒的东西  你害怕再次暴走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  老实说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟第一次接触就那情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你7岁时做感应测试用的「SLASH BREATH」  打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你能打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的双亲在「Society」将它登录成了你的专用遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们为此付出了不少努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜之前收集的遗物几乎全都寄赠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事  我当时可是没有试出任何反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们相信龙司一定能用好它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SLASH BREATH」是用龙牙制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟黑龙战斗就只能用它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道它拥有多大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你能再试一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝之所以会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为当时爸爸他们来救我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要激发藏在剑中的宝物  集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  想感谢她救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想为伤害了她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想再一次见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  借给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司…龙司！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是红龙  雾的效果已经散去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回龙司的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要龙司以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就杀了他好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么喜欢他  那就把他的头摘给你好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了他吧  人类和龙是绝对无法共存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对自己以外的种族存有偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他对你示爱了吗  说过喜欢你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类讨厌龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们有着毁灭世界的力量  他们害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人  龙司和英理子都很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可结果你还不是被带去「Society」了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不想让你在身边  嫌你碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃他吧  要不我就去杀了他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尼基斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有疑似「Society」的直升机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信号源  最终反应地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新东京泛用电波塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务是夺回实验对象  可照顾不到你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用您担心  我们是去救萝丝而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位都友好点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  最危险的不就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对研究来说可是不可多得的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计器异常  计器异常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法接近新东京泛用电波塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其周边发生着未知磁场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的结界吧  果然是还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由空中入侵不太现实  先降落到地面…唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计器恢复  磁场消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  挺厉害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是想着要救萝丝  它就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这塔里没有其他人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经装修完毕  但是还没对外开放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个做为暂定基地的好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音感应雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是龙鳞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候混进来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到  塔的中央有一股强大的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萝丝  还是奥尼基斯  还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意真方便啊  你也越来越熟悉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得  萝丝之所以粘上龙司…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  印刻效应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是一见钟情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上了小时候的龙司  想见你所以才到这来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙类哪有这样的感情侧面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能确定没有吗  见过萝丝之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲斐那家伙  干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该我问你才对  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是订契约前的气氛渲染吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙类竟然会有这种习性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了我明白了  那就由公主亲自跟他说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  跟英理子一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  不要再管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事  你们只会把我们当实验材料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也只会把你们当下等生物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙和龙在一起才是最好的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说得明白些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道人类讨厌龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌人类  也讨厌龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.21,0:15:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌讨厌  非常讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我  喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝也喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  喜欢你喜欢你喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你喜欢你喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻舞  冰雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英理子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你保护好萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首饰就是婚约的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种烂剑怎么可能打得开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚约解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太嚣张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够  你应该还有更强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  重新斟酌下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类怎么可能跟龙在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不会得到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运让我们战斗  厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些跟我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.49,0:18:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有话跟她说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙的吐息  能治愈人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我其实是本本族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么忙都帮不上  就老实开车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你  喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝  看够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙司  我在这下车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我在一起  奥尼基斯又会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找不到尸体  大概还没死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给龙司添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  或许他会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要变得更强  强到可以在萝丝身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在萝丝身边  所以才不是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟我在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  龙司好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你喜欢你喜欢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  该谁去负责解释啊？
